sources.description:
2012 Ice Age - A volcanic eruption in Iceland sets a massive glacier hurtling towards North America, freezing everything in its devastating path. As the impending ice age encroaches, a desperate family man fights to outrun the onslaught and escape the looming disaster.
2012.  Stars: Patrick Labyorteaux, Julie McCullough, Katie Wilson
